channel.title: Read this to the solution to moparscape
channel.description:
ok well i cant take the credit a web developer helped me out :)
ok heres what u do
zezumascape.com/mopar.jar
Download and run.
If that link is broekn, try zezumascape.com/moparscape.jar
And if worst comes to worst, moparisthebest.com/moparscape.html
its like a 2 second run then moparscape 3.2 w/ aryan should come up and u can play =)
dont forget enable java!![br][size=1]Posted on: August 18, 2007, 01:21:11 PM[/size][hr]the 2nd link worked fine 4 me a pop up will come and itll say .. open save or cancel click open and itll open moparscape for you ;D ;D
HAVE FUN! ;)
